description:
Kavanaugh is headline news. Jennifer Hudson and Chrissy Teigan are in Entertainment News. Nephew Tommy is in Nashville and calls in. Today's Strawberry Letter involves cheating and it gets complicated. Pimpin' talks to the crew about NFL week 4. Today in Closing Remarks, Big Dog talks about whether the grass is greener on the other side or not plus more.
